cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.RO 

The paper proposes a system based on machine learning for animal detection in semi-arid Savanna using UAVs. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of machine learning also suggests that the paper could belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of UAVs suggests that the paper could also belong to the graphics (cs.GR) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories.
